room_title: Escape room "Biohazard" by Race to Escape in Tampa
room_address: 2435 US Highway 19 N Suite 101 Holiday, FL 34691
room_description: A viral pandemic has swept across the world turning people into flesh-eating zombies. Billions of lives have already been lost and billions more are still at stake. Humanity is facing extinction. You are the last remaining scientists at the World Health Organization (WHO) in Geneva, Switzerland. You are tasked to complete development of a cure to the devastating virus. If you fail, all of humanity will be lost.
